card.desc:
skimlink: 
SELECT SUBSTRING_INDEX(SUBSTRING_INDEX(SUBSTRING_INDEX(SUBSTRING_INDEX(remote_referer, '/', 3), '://', -1), '/', 1), '?', 1) AS domain ,
sum(commission_value)/100 AS sum_commission_value, count(*) AS sales, merchant_name, country
 FROM sa_skimlinks_commission 
 WHERE `click_time` >= '2018-09-24' 
AND `click_time`< '2018-10-25' 
AND country IS NOT NULL  
GROUP BY domain_id, country
ORDER BY domain_id

SELECT SUBSTRING_INDEX(SUBSTRING_INDEX(SUBSTRING_INDEX(SUBSTRING_INDEX(remote_referer, '/', 3), '://', -1), '/', 1), '?', 1) AS domain ,
sum(commission_value)/100 AS sum_commission_value, count(*) AS sales, merchant_name, country
 FROM sa_flexoffer_sale 
 WHERE `transaction_date` >= '2018-10-24' 
AND `transaction_date`< '2018-11-25' 
AND country IS NOT NULL  
GROUP BY domain_id, country
ORDER BY domain_id

GROUP BY campaign_id, merchant_id, country

sum(commission_value)/100 AS sum_commission_value, count(*) AS sales, merchant_name, country
 FROM sa_skimlinks_commission

AND `click_time`< '2018-10-25' 
AND country IS NOT NULL  
GROUP BY domain_id, country
ORDER BY domain_id

rpm -ivh https://repo.zabbix.com/zabbix/4.0/rhel/6/x86_64/zabbix-release-4.0-1.el6.noarch.rpm	
yum install zabbix-agent -y	
vi /etc/zabbix/zabbix_agentd.conf	
Sửa Server=127.0.0.1 thành Server=127.0.0.1,server-monitor.megaads.vn
service zabbix-agent restart



Cách mở cổng zabbix 10050
Centos 6 
iptables -A INPUT -p tcp -m tcp --dport 10050 -j ACCEPT
service iptables save
Centos 7 
sudo ufw allow 10050/tcp
sudo firewall-cmd --add-port=10050/tcp
sudo firewall-cmd --add-port=10050/tcp --permanent

Test đã được chưa 
telnet <client_ip> 10050
 từ server-monitor. hoặc gõ lệnh
zabbix_get -s <client_ip> -k "vfs.fs.size[/,free]"
